request.description:
Detailed health check with service status.

Response:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "status": "healthy",
    "version": "6.0.0",
    "timestamp": "2026-07-15T...",
    "uptime": 1234.56,
    "services": {
      "backend": "running",
      "database": "connected",
      "ai": "loaded",
      "websocket": "active"
    }
  }
}
```

Get historical spatial occupancy data.

Query params:
- hours: number of hours to look back (default: 24)
- car_id: filter by car ID (optional)

Response:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "query": { "hours": 24, "carId": 4 },
    "records": [
      {
        "timestamp": "2026-07-15T...",
        "carId": 4,
        "occupancyRatio": 0.72,
        "freeSpaceRatio": 0.28,
        "densityIndicator": "RED"
      }
    ],
    "summary": {
      "averageOccupancy": 0.65,
      "peakOccupancy": 0.92,
      "peakTime": "08:30",
      "totalRecords": 24
    }
  }
}
```

