Get camera to train car mapping lookup table.

Response (40 cameras, 4 per car):
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "mappings": [
      { "cameraId": "car01_cam01", "zone": "car_1_front_left", "carId": 1, "type": "ceiling_fisheye", "position": "front_left" },
      { "cameraId": "car01_cam02", "zone": "car_1_front_right", "carId": 1, "type": "ceiling_fisheye", "position": "front_right" },
      { "cameraId": "car01_cam03", "zone": "car_1_rear_left", "carId": 1, "type": "ceiling_fisheye", "position": "rear_left" },
      { "cameraId": "car01_cam04", "zone": "car_1_rear_right", "carId": 1, "type": "ceiling_fisheye", "position": "rear_right" },
      ...
      { "cameraId": "car10_cam04", "zone": "car_10_rear_right", "carId": 10, "type": "ceiling_fisheye", "position": "rear_right" }
    ]
  }
}
```

Reset simulation to initial state.

Clears all train data, warnings, and decisions.
Broadcasts 'simulation_reset' event via WebSocket.

Response:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "message": "Simulation reset successfully",
    "timestamp": "2026-07-15T..."
  }
}
```
